# Control Flow Quiz App
This is a quiz application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for the front-end, Python for the back-end, and a JSON file to store the quiz questions. The topic of this quiz app is control flow, and there are 25 questions in total.

# Features
 1 Interactive user interface for taking the quiz
 2 Randomized order of questions for each quiz attempt
 3 Display of final score at the end of the quiz
 4 Option to retake the quiz or go back to the home page
 
# Files
-> quiz.html: The HTML file containing the structure of the quiz app
-> style.css: The CSS file containing the styling of the quiz app
-> script.js: The JavaScript file containing the logic and interactivity of the quiz app
-> questions.json: The JSON file containing the quiz questions and their respective answers and options
-> app.py: The Python file containing the server-side code for serving the quiz app and processing quiz submissions

# Usage
To use this quiz app, simply clone or download the repository and open the quiz.html file in a web browser. Alternatively, you can run the app.py file using Python to serve the quiz app on a local web server.
